---
title: Peanut Confit Duck Bao with Sesame Wedges and Sambal Cucumber Slaw
description: Stuffed full of flavour, these Peanut Confit Duck Bao are a fusion favourite. Complimented by two delicious sides, these brilliant bao are destined to be a treat for your table.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R38_W29_UK_SBN15838-3_MAIN_F4_low-b6ebc5fc.jpg
